text: ZIS may refer to: * Zavod imeni Likhacheva of Moscow, formerly Automotive Factory No. 2 Zavod imeni Stalina, and its products * Artillery Factory No. 92, Zavod imeni Stalina of Gorky, and its products * Zentrum für Internationale Studien der TU Dresden, School of International Studies of the Dresden University of Technology in Germany * Zhuhai International School in Zhuhai, China * Zurich International School in Zurich, Switzerland * Zingiberene synthase, an enzyme
title: ZIS
